                            <li> Development of PC applications for software development.                                </li>
                            <li> Development of other PC applications.                                                   </li>
                        </ul>
                    </td>
                    <td>
                        <ul style="text-align:left">
                            <li> Thai Nationality</li>
                            <li> Female, Male.</li>
                            <li> Age above 23 years old. Fresh graduates are also welcomed.</li>
                            <li> Graduation Bachelor Degree in Electrical Engineering, Electronics Engineering, Computer Engineering,Computer Science or related field</li>
                            <li> Programming skill C language.</li>
                            <li> English Proficiency in conversation level is preferred</li>
                        </ul>
